     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "generated" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ConceptMap TIFLOW-CM-TelemetryDataStatusCodes</b></p><a name=\"TIFLOW-CM-TelemetryDataStatusCodes\"> </a><a name=\"hcTIFLOW-CM-TelemetryDataStatusCodes\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Group 1 </b>Mapping from <code>https://gematik.de/fhir/erp/CodeSystem/tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs</code> to <code>ti-flow-telemetriedaten-statuscodes</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_OCSP_BACKEND_ERROR</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79001</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_ACCESSCODE_MISMATCH</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79200</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_ACCESS_CODE_INVALID</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79201</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_ACCESS_PERMISSION_INVALID</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79202</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_ALTERNATIVE_IK_FORBIDDEN</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79203</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_AUTH_NOT_OWNER</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79204</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_AUTH_ROLE_NOT_ALLOWED</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79205