r/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79240</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_CHARGEITEM_DISPENSE_SIGNATURE_INVALID</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79241</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_CHARGEITEM_ID_REQUIRED</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79242</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_CHARGEITEM_NOT_FOUND</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79243</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 3 </b>Mapping from <code>https://gematik.de/fhir/erp/CodeSystem/tiflow-xborder-operation-outcome-details-cs</code> to <code>ti-flow-telemetriedaten-statuscodes</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_XBORDER_COUNTRY_CODE_INVALID</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79244</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_XBORDER_NOT_ACTIVATED</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79245</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_XBORDER_NO_PRESCRIPTIONS_FOUND</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79246</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 4 </b>Mapping from <code>https://gematik.de/fhir/erp/CodeSystem/tiflow-erezept-operation-outcome-details-cs</code> to <code>ti-flow-telemetriedaten-statuscodes</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_EREZEPT_DRUG_CATEGORY_FORBIDDEN</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79247</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_EREZEPT_MVO_ENDDATE_INVALID</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79248</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_EREZEPT_MVO_FLOWTYPE_INVALID</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79249</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_EREZEPT_MVO_ID_INVALID</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79250</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_EREZEPT_MVO_INVALID</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79251</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_EREZEPT_MVO_NOT_VALID</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79252</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_EREZEPT_MVO_STARTDATE_INVALID</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79253</td></tr><tr><td>TIFLOW_EREZEPT_PZN_INVALID</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79254</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 5 </b>Mapping from <code>json-fehlercodes</code> to <code>ti-flow-telemetriedaten-statuscodes</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>invalidOid</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>79262</td></tr><tr><td>methodNotAllo